snippet.title: Airspace Defender - UploadVR Showcase Winter 2024 | Meta Quest Mixed Reality
snippet.description:
UploadVR article:
https://www.uploadvr.com/airspace-defender-adds-depth-in-new-gameplay-update/

Airspace Defender is a 3D tabletop arcade game in mixed reality. Manage your city's defenses and thwart enemy attacks with carefully timed retaliatory strikes!

Wishlist Airspace Defender on Meta Quest:
https://vr.meta.me/s/1YLaztRrTqR5ojs

Be sure to join our Discord for exclusive content, friendly banter, and the latest news straight from the devs!
https://www.notsuspicious.biz/discord

Leaderboards & More:
https://www.notsuspicious.biz/airspace-defender

Recorded on #MetaQuest3. Available on #MetaQuest2, #MetaQuestPro and #MetaQuest3 family!
